    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. Power is delivered via the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a linear, high-revving power band. The chassis is exceptionally taut, benefiting from documented rear subframe reinforcement and a precise Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox. This example remains in collector-grade condition with original paint depth, pristine bushings, and a limited-slip differential that remains tight and responsive. Recent preventative maintenance includes rod bearing replacement and a full cooling system overhaul. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
